<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Fell3" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Fell,</orth> vb. to hew down: <cit><quote>--ed my woods,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 3.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 1, 23</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 1, 210</bibl>. <cit><quote>I'll f. thee down,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.2.123" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 2, 123</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ed him dead,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.2.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 2, 76</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>all save thee I f. with curses,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.508" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 508</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>